  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Computerized Cognitive Training in Adults With ADHD: Change in ADHD Symptoms, Executive Functions and Quality of Life Following Three Months of Training.</brief_title>
  <official_title>ADHD Symptoms, Executive Functions and Quality of Life Following Three Months of Training.</official_title>
